title: Mark Levin Audio Rewind - 12/23/19
description:
On Monday's Mark Levin Show, KARN Radio Host Doc Washburn fills in. Rudy Giuliani should visit Arkansas for Hunter Biden's baby's mother hearing for the sake of making a statement about where's Hunter? Then, U.S Attorney General Bill Barr rejects the policies that weaken police. Barr challenges former FBI Director James Comey's statement that the FBI's lapses were due to sloppiness, not malfeasance. Later, it's been said on this program that Nancy Pelosi's abuse of power is unconstitutional.
